supportedObjects.name: Device
supportedObjects.description: This LwM2M Object provides a range of device related information which can be queried by the LwM2M Server, and a device reboot and factory reset function.

supportedObjects.name: CmdhPolicy
supportedObjects.description: This Object provides links to a set of rules associated with a specific CSE that governs the behavior of that CSE regarding rejecting, buffering and sending request or response messages via the Mcc reference point.
